---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Terms of Use — LinkKeep" description="LinkKeep terms and conditions of use.">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-(--muted)">Last updated: June 24, 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-(--muted) leading-relaxed">
      <p>By downloading or using LinkKeep ("the App"), you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the App.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-(--foreground)">Use of the App</h2>
      <p>LinkKeep is a personal tool to save, organize, and verify the status of web links. The App is designed for personal, non-commercial use.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-(--foreground)">Link verification</h2>
      <p>Status verification is based on HTTP responses from destination servers. We do not guarantee the accuracy of results, as servers may respond differently depending on context.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-(--foreground)">Data and responsibility</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>All data is stored locally on your device.</li>
        <li>You are responsible for maintaining backups of your data.</li>
        <li>We are not responsible for data loss due to app deletion, device failure, or operating system updates.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-(--foreground)">Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>The App, its design, code, and visual identity are property of Florex Labs. Reproduction, distribution, or modification without authorization is not permitted.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-(--foreground)">Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>The App is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. Florex Labs shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, or consequential damages arising from the use of the App.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-(--foreground)">Changes to terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with the updated date.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-(--foreground)">Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:hello@florexlabs.com" class="text-(--brand) hover:underline">hello@florexlabs.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
